OL,3,CGreat grandma spared jail after fatal
OL,4,Cmobility scooter crash
OL,6,FA great grandmother who killed a
OL,7,Fmobility scooter rider in a crash on a
OL,8,Fpedestrian crossing has been spared an
OL,9,Fimmediate prison sentence.
OL,11,FAnn Fletcher, 86, collided with 61-
OL,12,Fyear-old double amputee Mark Jackson
OL,13,Fon Broad Street in Grantham,
OL,14,FLincolnshire, causing him to be thrown
OL,15,Fto the ground.
OL,17,FMr Jackson died the next day.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
