PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1782559108
OL,3,CGreat grandma spared jail after fatal
OL,4,Cmobility scooter crash
OL,6,FFletcher, of Hallfield Crescent,
OL,7,FHonington, pleaded guilty to causing
OL,8,Fhis death by careless driving and was
OL,9,Fsentenced to 16 weeks in prison,
OL,10,Fsuspended for two years.
OL,12,FLincoln Crown Court heard Mr Jackson
OL,13,Fwas using a toucan crossing while the
OL,14,Flight was still red when the accident
OL,15,Fhappened on 14 August 2024.
OL,17,FProsecutor Dale Brook said Fletcher's
OL,18,Fview was initially obscured by another
OL,19,Fpedestrian and then the A-frame in her
OL,20,Fcar, but she failed to move her head.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1782559108
OL,3,CGreat grandma spared jail after fatal
OL,4,Cmobility scooter crash
OL,6,F"After Mr Jackson became visible she
OL,7,Fdid not apply her brakes," Mr Brook
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,FA driver who was travelling behind
OL,11,FFletcher told police he saw Mr Jackson
OL,12,Fon the crossing and had expected
OL,13,FFletcher to break.
OL,15,FMr Brook said it was a "momentary
OL,16,Flapse of concentration"
OL,18,F"The aggravating feature is Mr Jackson
OL,19,Fwas a vulnerable road user as a
OL,20,Fpedestrian, as a disabled mobility
OL,21,Fscooter rider," he added.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1782559108
OL,3,CGreat grandma spared jail after fatal
OL,4,Cmobility scooter crash
OL,6,FMr Jackson, who had both legs
OL,7,Famputated in 2023, died in hospital
OL,8,Fthe next day from complications.
OL,10,FOne witness to the collision heard
OL,11,FFletcher say: "He just came out of
OL,12,Fnowhere."
OL,14,FIn a victim impact statement Mr
OL,15,FJackson's teenage son said it felt
OL,16,F"like my heart had stopped" when he
OL,17,Fheard about the collision.
OL,19,F"Life has not been the same since dad
OL,20,Fpassed away," his daughter added.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1782559108
OL,3,CGreat grandma spared jail after fatal
OL,4,Cmobility scooter crash
OL,6,FTom Gent, mitigating for Fletcher,
OL,7,Fsaid the incident "haunted her daily".
OL,9,F"This defendant is consumed with
OL,10,Fremorse," he said.
OL,12,FFletcher, a widow who used a walking
OL,13,Fframe to enter the court dock, sat
OL,14,Fwith her head bowed as Recorder Luke
OL,15,FBlackburn passed sentence.
OL,17,FHe said that while it was unclear if
OL,18,FFletcher's deteriorating eyesight
OL,19,Fcontributed to the collision, all
OL,20,Fdrivers had a duty to ensure they were
OL,21,Fsafe.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1782559108
OL,3,CGreat grandma spared jail after fatal
OL,4,Cmobility scooter crash
OL,6,F"What I can say is that Mr Jackson was
OL,7,Fthere to be seen," he added.
OL,9,FFletcher was also banned from driving
OL,10,Ffor two years, and must take an
OL,11,Fextended retest before she can drive
OL,12,Fagain.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
